text: Shweta Bhattacharya (born 21 September 1992) is an Indian television actress. She has acted in television programs such as Jamuna Dhaki, Sindoorkhela, Joy Kanhaiya Lal Ki and Tumi Robe Nirobe. == Television programs == * Kanak Kakon * Jarowar Jhumko * Sindoor Khela * Tumi Robe Nirobe * Joy Kanhaiya Lal Ki * Jamuna Dhaki == References == == Other websites == * * Category:Living people Category:1992 births Category:Indian television actors
